general.description:
I act for and provide advice to public and private sector clients, allowing them to resolve their employment problems with limited business disruption. 

My employment/industrial law expertise includes:

- Employee claims (unfair dismissals, general protections and workplace bullying);
- Enterprise bargaining and union engagement;
- Employment contracts, policies and Modern Awards;
- Performance management;
- Management of ill or injured employees;
- Termination (performance, capacity or conduct);
- Workplace surveillance and privacy; 
- Employee transfer during takeovers, mergers, and acquisition; and
- Restraint of trade.

